Description: Transitional package for Final Burn Alpha
 This is a transitional dummy package for Final Burn Alpha to whom comes from
 hunterks PPA. It can safely be removed.

Package: libretro-fba-cps1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libretro-core-info
Description: Libretro wrapper for Final Burn Alpha CPS1 core
 This wrapper makes Final Burn Alpha API compatible with libretro, thus allowing
 its use with libretro frontends, such as RetroArch.
 .
 This package provides the CPS1 core from Final Burn Alpha.

